### Voxemo API — VS Code REST Client
### Install "REST Client" extension (humao.rest-client) to use these

@base_url = http://localhost:8000

# ─────────────────────────────────────────
# Health Check
# ─────────────────────────────────────────

### GET /health
GET {{base_url}}/health
Accept: application/json

###

# ─────────────────────────────────────────
# Predict Emotion from WAV file
# ─────────────────────────────────────────

### POST /predict — upload a local WAV file
POST {{base_url}}/predict
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----Boundary

------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test.wav"
Content-Type: audio/wav

< ./backend/test.wav
------Boundary--

###
